      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_ratansi_arVol02Doc09.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>بسم الله الرحمن الرحیم</p>
         </div>

         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
            <p>In the name of God, the most gracious, the most compassionate</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="ara" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>اقر
               <persName ref="#abdullahAlBalushi">عبدالله بن شهدات البلوشي</persName>
                ان عليه
               <persName ref="#ratansi">للسيت رطنسيه
                  <lb/>بن برسوتم البنياني</persName>
               <measure type="currency" unit="qurush" quantity="53">ثلاثة و خمسين قرشا فضة
                  افرنسياً</measure>
               <lb/>و
               <measure type="currency" unit="qurush" quantity="1/2">نصف قرش فضة افرنسيسي</measure>
                حقا مؤجلاً عنه لمضي ستة
               <lb/>اشهر زمانا من اليوم اقرارا منه بذالك بتاريخ يوم
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>٢٥</num> 
               شهر ذي
               <lb/>الحجة الحرام سنة
               <num>١٣١٣</num></date>
               و كتبه
               <persName ref="#riyami">ناصر بن عامر بن سليمان الريامي</persName>
                بيده
               <lb/> بمعرفة
               <persName ref="#ilyas">الياس بن فقير</persName>
                و
               <persName ref="#ghulamBalushi">غلام شاه</persName>
                البلوشيين </p>
         </div>

         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/><persName ref="#abdullahAlBalushi">Abdullah bin Shuhadat Al-Balushi</persName>
                acknowledges that upon him to the
               <persName ref="#ratansi">Seth Ratansi
                  <lb/>Bin Purshottam Al-Banyani</persName>
                [is]
               <measure type="currency" unit="qurush" quantity="53">three and fifty French silver
                  <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qirsh">qurush</ref></measure>
               <lb/>and
               <measure type="currency" unit="qurush" quantity="1/2">half a French silver
                  <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qirsh">qirsh</ref></measure>,
               an obligation that is deferred from him for six
               <lb/>months’ time from today, an acknowledgement from him of that on
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">25 Dhu
                <lb/>Al-Hijja Al-Haram 1313</date><note>Arabic transliteration of the month is used here because the document is fully in Arabic. This month is spelled Zi al-hijja elsewhere on the site in accordance with Persian usage.</note>
               and
               <persName ref="#riyami">Nasser bin Amer bin Sulaiman Al-Riyami</persName>
                wrote it with his own hand
               <lb/>with the cognizance of
               <persName ref="#ilyas">Ilyas bin Faqir</persName>
                and
               <persName ref="#ghulamBalushi">Ghulam Shah</persName>
                Al-Balushiyin (the Baluchis)
            </p>
         </div>
